@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qcelnv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.07 / tmp + 0.90)) * (v2 - wp.abs(tmp + 0.87)))
    v0 = wp.sin(v2)
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.exp(v2 + 0.12) / (v1 + 0.11 * v1 + 0.58)))
    tmp = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.54 + v1 + 0.52)) - ((tmp + 0.39 / tmp + 0.46) * (tmp + 0.72 / v0 + 0.59)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.55 - v2 + 0.64)) + v2)
    data[tid] = v0
